</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="400">2.1. Setting up shipping profiles</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Proceed as follows to set up shipping profiles for Hood.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Setting up shipping profiles:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » System settings » Markets » Hood</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Scroll down to the <strong>Shipping profiles</strong> section and click on the <strong>New</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter a <strong>name</strong> for the shipping profile.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a <strong>region</strong> from the drop-down list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a <strong>shipping method</strong> from the drop-down list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the <strong>shipping costs</strong>.<br>
→ Enter any additional shipping methods and shipping costs for this region.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.<br>
→ The shipping profile is displayed in the <strong>Overview</strong> tab. It can be edited or deleted there.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Create further shipping profiles in the same way. The shipping profiles are then available in the <strong>Base</strong> tab of a <a href="#Creating listings">listing</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="450">2.2. Linking shipping profiles</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to the menu <strong>System » System settings » Markets » Hood » Shipping profile links</strong> to link shipping methods to a shipping profile. Settings carried out in this menu are taken into consideration during the order import. If you do not link the shipping method, the shipping profile calculation is carried out automatically. Proceed as described below in order to link shipping methods to a shipping profile.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Linking shipping profiles:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » System settings » Markets » Hood » Shipping profile links</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a <strong>Shipping profile</strong> for the desired shipping method from the drop-down list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="500">2.3. Setting up payment methods</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up the payment methods that you want to use for this market. This is done within your account on Hood. Choose between different options such as bank transfer (cash in advance), purchase on invoice, or PayPal. The payment methods are then available in the listing.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="600">2.4. Automatically posting feedback</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter your feedback texts first. Then set up an <a href="/en/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a> to automatically send your feedback texts to your buyers. All buyers who gave you feedback then automatically receive a random feedback text in return.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Entering feedback texts:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » System settings » Markets » Hood</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter up to four feedback texts in the <strong>Automatic feedback</strong> area. <br>
→ These texts are chosen randomly.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
