</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Add event procedure</strong>.<br>
→ The <strong>Create new event procedure</strong> window opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter a name.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the <strong>event</strong> listed in <a href="#automatic-feedback">Table 2</a> below.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.<br>
→ The event is created.</p>
</li>
