<p>Create any number of directories or subdirectories for organising your listings.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating directories:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » System settings » Listings » Directories</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>New directory</strong> tab.</p>
