<h2 id="4000">9. Starting listings</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Listings can be started in several ways. Start individual listings manually. Multiple listings can be started automatically using listing schedulers or endless listers. Items are exported when starting listings.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Learn more about <strong>starting listings</strong> in the following video tutorial:</p>
