<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select one of the following options: <strong>ALL</strong>, <strong>Title</strong>, <strong>Subtitle</strong>, <strong>Category</strong>, <strong>Item details</strong>, <strong>Duration</strong>, <strong>Shipping information</strong>, <strong>Description</strong>, <strong>Images</strong>, <strong>Variations</strong>, <strong>Price</strong>, <strong>Payment methods</strong>.<br>
The <strong>None</strong> option must be activated in the <strong>Procedures</strong> area.</p></td>
</tr>
