</table>
<div class="admonitionblock tip">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-tip" title="Tip"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Query update status</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can query the update status once you have begun updating the listings. Click on <strong>Query update status</strong>. The results are displayed in a message.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
